quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  2,258,Ona noted jeden Have argued Abraham jeho Lord GOD dat him kingship? Abraham said Moj Lord grants zivot smrt. He said ja grant zivot smrt. Abraham said GOD brings sun east mozem ona bring it zapad? disbeliever stumped GOD NIE guide the ZLOMYSELNY
  2,259,"Consider jeden ist okolo ghost town zazrak Ako mozem GOD revive this it umrel? GOD potom put him smrt 100 rocnik potom resurrected him! He said \"Ako long have ona zostat tu? He said ja je tu dni part dni. He nie said Ona bol tu sto rocnik. look do tvoj food pne; they nie spoil Look tvoj donkey -My thus render ona lekcia ludia. ihned note ako my zostrojit bones potom pokryvka them ani. ryba. ani. rak. When he realized co happened he said Teraz ja zauzlit lenze GOD bol Omnipotent"
  2,260,Abraham said Moj Lord show mna ako Ona revive dead He said Robit ona nie verit? He said Ano Ja zelat si reassure moj srdce. He said Berie 4 birds study ich oznacit miesto a kusok z each bird hill potom vola sa them do ona! They pojdem ona v a ponahlajte sa Ona zauzlit lenze GOD bol Almighty Wise